        public boolean validateEvent(net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.message.guild.GuildMessageReceivedEvent event,
                             CommandSettings settings)
        Checks if a GuildMessageReceivedEvent matches all requirements given by a CommandSettings object. This method gets invoked on every incoming GuildMessageReceivedEvent.
        Parameters:
        event - the corresponding GuildMessageReceivedEvent
        settings - the CommandSettings
        Returns:
        true if the event is valid

      • parseEvent

        public java.lang.String[] parseEvent(net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.message.guild.GuildMessageReceivedEvent event,
                                     CommandSettings settings)
        Parses an GuildMessageReceivedEvent by removing whitespaces and the prefix from the message and then splitting it at each blank space. This method gets invoked if an event is valid and thus ready to be processed.
        Parameters:
        event - the corresponding GuildMessageReceivedEvent
        settings - the CommandSettings
        Returns:
        the split user input
